import React,{Component} from 'react' var mealtypeurl = "http://localhost:8900/mealtype"; class QuickSearchDisplay extends Component{ constructor(){ super() this.state={ mealtype:"" } } handleQuickCards = (data) => { } render(){ return(
{this.handleQuickCards(this.state.mealtype)}
) } componentDidMount(){ fetch(mealtypeurl,{method:'GET'}).then((res) => res.json()).then((data) => { this.setState({mealtype:data}) }) } } export default QuickSearchDisplay
